{"id":288968,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/04/global-voices-照片集：马达加斯加的往事/","date":"2013-04-14T02:45:13Z","modified":"2013-04-14T02:45:13Z","title":"Global Voices | 照片集：马达加斯加的往事","content":"<p><p>非洲的历史相当丰富，但往往<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2012/06/20/rediscovering-africas-forgotten-history/\">鲜少记录在案</a>。为了补齐马达加斯加的这些缺漏，民间团体已经开始执行<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2012/10/23/madagascar-preserving-national-heritage-with-video-archiving/\">数位化保存</a>马达加斯加历史事件的计划。</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/MadagascarHier?ref=ts&#038;fref=ts\">Madagascar Hier</a>（马达加斯加的昨日）以及<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/IlEtaitUneFoisMadagascar\">Il était une fois Madagascar</a>（马达加斯加的往事）这两个Facebook专页，抱持着荣耀及保存马达加斯加历史的同一愿望，替各个城市及马达加斯加人民的古老照片“存档”。</div>\n<div>在此搜集了一些贴在专页上面的照片，它们不仅描绘了一个不太遥远的过去，也激起我们对简朴时光的怀旧情感，当时日常生活的困苦及贫穷似乎还不那么显而易见。若想观看更多照片，请造访他们的Facebook专页。</div>\n<p>首都塔那那利佛的照片</p>\n<p>Andohalo花园</p>\n<p><div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=439075662827648&#038;set=a.439074472827767.99599.439052299496651&#038;type=3&#038;theater\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-141341\" alt=\"Jardin Andohalo — at Antananarivo sur Madagascar Hier \" src=\"http://fr.globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/antananarivo-andohalo-vintage-375x277.jpg\" width=\"375\" height=\"277\" /></a></p>\n<p>首都的Andohalo花园（<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=439075662827648&#038;set=a.439074472827767.99599.439052299496651&#038;type=3&#038;theater\">Garden of Andohalo</a>法），照片转贴自Madagascar Hier</p>\n</div>\n<p>Ankatso大学</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=439193716149176&#038;set=a.439193692815845.99619.439052299496651&#038;type=3&#038;theater\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-141343\" alt=\"L'Université d'Anakatso à Antananarivo sur Il était une fois Madagascar \" src=\"http://fr.globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Ankatso-vintage-375x285.jpg\" width=\"375\" height=\"285\" /></a></p>\n<p>首都的Ankatso大学</p>\n</div>\n<p>Zoma街市</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=510966325612482&#038;set=a.510662255642889.1073741825.505039766205138&#038;type=3&#038;theater\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-141344\" alt=\"zoma vintage\" src=\"http://fr.globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/zoma-vintage-375x254.jpg\" width=\"375\" height=\"254\" /></a></p>\n<p>Zoma街市，照片转贴自Il était une fois Madagascar</p>\n</div>\n<p>东岸城市图阿马西那</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=447398801995334&#038;set=pb.439052299496651.-2207520000.1363537910&#038;type=3&#038;theater\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-141345\" alt=\"Toamasina, rue du commerce \" src=\"http://fr.globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Toamasina-vintage-375x244.jpg\" width=\"375\" height=\"244\" /></a></p>\n<p>图阿马西那的商业街</p>\n</div>\n<p>年轻的贝齐米萨拉卡（Betsimisaraka）女孩<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2013/03/21/once-upon-a-time-in-madagascar/jeune%20fille%20betsimisaraka\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://fr.globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/jeune-fille-betsimisaraka-197x300.jpg\" /></a></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-141346\" alt=\"jeune fille Betsimisaraka\" src=\"http://fr.globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/jeune-fille-betsimisaraka-197x300.jpg\" width=\"197\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<p>年轻的贝齐米萨拉卡女孩</p>\n</div>\n<p><strong><br />西岸城市马哈赞加</strong></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=446686648733216&#038;set=a.446686212066593.1073741831.439052299496651&#038;type=3&#038;theater\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-141348\" alt=\"Mahajanga , le bord de mer \" src=\"http://fr.globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Mahajanga-vintage-375x245.jpg\" width=\"375\" height=\"245\" /></a></p>\n<p>马哈赞加海岸，庞加莱大道（Boulevard Poincaré）</p>\n</div>\n<p>马达加斯加南部城市菲亚那兰楚阿</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=443322625736285&#038;set=a.443322499069631.1073741828.439052299496651&#038;type=3&#038;theater\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-141349\" alt=\"Fianaratsoa\" src=\"http://fr.globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/fianaratsoa-vintage-375x249.jpg\" width=\"375\" height=\"249\" /></a></p>\n<p>菲亚那兰楚阿市政厅</p>\n</div>\n<p>马达加斯加南部的安坦德罗（Antandroy）舞者</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=444349402300274&#038;set=a.444349172300297.1073741830.439052299496651&#038;type=3&#038;theater\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-141353\" alt=\"Danseurs Antadroy dans le Sud de Madagascar \" src=\"http://fr.globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/antadroy-vintage-375x261.jpg\" width=\"375\" height=\"261\" /></a></p>\n<p>马达加斯加南部的安坦德罗舞者</p>\n</div>\n<p>马达加斯加北部城市安齐拉纳纳</p>\n<p>Cap Diego</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=441696112565603&#038;set=a.441695899232291.1073741826.439052299496651&#038;type=3&#038;theater\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-141350\" alt=\"Antsiranana - Le Cap Diégo \" src=\"http://fr.globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/diego-375x241.jpg\" width=\"375\" height=\"241\" /></a></p>\n<p>Cap Diego，安齐拉纳纳</p>\n</div>\n<p><strong>马达加斯加1895年殖民战争的图像</strong></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=440808249321056&#038;set=a.440808202654394.1073741825.439052299496651&#038;type=3&#038;theater\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-141351\" alt=\"Illustration du Petit Journal sur la guerre coloniale à Madagascar \" src=\"http://fr.globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/colonisation-de-madagascar-202x300.jpg\" width=\"202\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<p>法国画报《Le Petit Journal》关于马达加斯加殖民战争的插图</p>\n</div>\n<p>这两项倡议，以及其他努力保存马达加斯加历史的计划，都很值得注意。读者也提供国内其他地区的照片给这些专页。</p>\n<div>校对者：Ameli</div>\n<p><span><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://fr.globalvoicesonline.org/author/lova-rakoto/\" title=\"文章导读 Rakotomalala\">Rakotomalala</a></span> · <span>译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/gvzhteam/\" title=\"文章导读 GV 中文化小组\">GV 中文化小组</a></span></span>  · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://fr.globalvoicesonline.org/2013/03/17/141304/\" title=\"阅读原文  fr\">阅读原文  fr</a></span> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2013/04/14/12364/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br />分享: <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87%E9%9B%86%EF%BC%9A%E9%A9%AC%E8%BE%BE%E5%8A%A0%E6%96%AF%E5%8A%A0%E7%9A%84%E5%BE%80%E4%BA%8B&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F04%2F14%2F12364%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F04%2F14%2F12364%2F&#038;desc=%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87%E9%9B%86%EF%BC%9A%E9%A9%AC%E8%BE%BE%E5%8A%A0%E6%96%AF%E5%8A%A0%E7%9A%84%E5%BE%80%E4%BA%8B\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/\" onclick=\"javascript:var js=document.createElement (\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F04%2F14%2F12364%2F\" title=\"facebook\"><span>facebook</span></a> ·